news_header: Trump suggests Ukraine might become Russian in the future.
news_original_title: Trump: ”Ukraina voi olla jonain päivänä venäläinen”
news_text: In a recent interview with Fox News, US President Donald Trump speculated on the future of Ukraine, suggesting it could one day be part of Russia. He mentioned that the US might seek natural resources from Ukraine in exchange for assistance, emphasizing a desire to reclaim financial investments.
